inence is the first observed in\nHe II 304 {\\AA} emission at such a great height (above 6 $R_\\sun$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2022 16:17:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
