ble\ntriangle algebra by B\\\" ockenhauer et al. based on the braided structure of the\ncategories and on $\\alpha$-induction. The introductory section of this paper to\nsubfactors and fusion categories has the character of a review.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2022 16:56:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 08:30:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
