ch effort in the rapidly growing field related to\nthe development of biomaterial scaffolds and lab-on-a-chip systems for NTE\napplications. Besides presenting recent advances achieved by NTE strategies,\nthis work also delineates existing limitations and highlights emerging\npossibilities and future prospects in this field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 09:21:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
