lly, the use of the AC-GAN Discriminator as a bot detector, has\noutperformed former ML approaches, showcasing the efficiency of our end to end\nframework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 11:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
