rom\nthe latter approach we perform a perturbation expansion. This allows us to\ncalculate analytically, up to linear order, the generalized temperature and the\ncorresponding heat exchange. By this, we provide explicit expressions and a\nphysical interpretation for the leading corrections induced by\nnon-Markovianity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 13:49:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 11:51:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
