 a good vision of the deformation\nof the myocardium during CPR. Using this method, it is possible to predict the\ndeformation of every part of the heart, especially right and left ventricles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2022 14:06:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
